# Pem mobile app (`app/`)

**Product:** **dump → organized extracts + thoughts journal**. Primary surface: **`/inbox`** (Daily Brief). Voice-first dump via inline bar, text secondary. **Intake bar** — user picks **Dump** or **Ask** (swipe/tap); same text/voice UI, different endpoints (`/dumps` vs `/ask`, including voice variants).

## Screens & navigation

- **Navigation:** **expo-router** **`Stack`** (`app/(app)/_layout.tsx`) + **`AppDrawerProvider`** / **`AppDrawerContent`** — simplified drawer:
  - **Main:** Brief · Dumps · Done
  - **Bottom:** Settings
- Batch/category pages accessible via batch chips on Brief or `/category/[slug]` route.
- **`thoughts/_layout.tsx`** inner **`Stack`** (list → detail). **`category/[slug].tsx`** dynamic category/batch page.
- **`AppMenuButton`** opens drawer; scrim closes.
- **Deleted screens:** `/dump`, `/dump-confirmed`, `/everything`, `/ask` — replaced by unified InlineVoiceBar + PemResponseSheet.

## TypeScript & components

- **TypeScript strict** — functional components only.
- **API:** **`lib/pemApi.ts`** — types: `ApiExtract`, `BriefResponse`, `LogEntry`, `AskPemResponse`, `ExtractsQueryParams`. Key functions: `getBrief`, `getExtractHistory`, `generateExtractDraft`, `patchExtractDone`/`Dismiss`/`Undone`/`Undismiss`/`Snooze`, `createDump`, `createVoiceDump`, `askPem`, `createVoiceAsk`, `getAskHistory`. Routes: `/inbox/brief`, `/dumps`, `/dumps/voice`, `/ask`, `/ask/voice`, `/ask/history`, `/extracts/...`.
- **Inbox UI tokens:** **`constants/inboxChrome.ts`** (light/dark glance surfaces); compose with **`ThemeContext`**.
- **Feature folders:** **`components/inbox/`** (InlineVoiceBar, PemResponseSheet, GlanceRow, ExtractDetailModal, InboxHeader, DumpSuccessOverlay), **`components/navigation/`** (drawer + menu button), **`components/ui/`** (`PemListRow`, `PemMindEmptyState`).
- **InlineVoiceBar:** Dump mode → **`POST /dumps`** / **`POST /dumps/voice`**. Ask mode → **`POST /ask`** / **`POST /ask/voice`** (never creates a dump). Callbacks: `onDumpSuccess`, `onDumpCreated`, `onPemResponse`. Bar modes: idle, recording (pause/resume), paused, text.
- **PemResponseSheet:** Slide-up sheet showing Pem's answer when user asks a question via the voice bar. Dismissible. Appears automatically from `onPemResponse` callback.
- **Daily Brief (InboxHomeScreen):** Time-based sections — overdue (red), today (amber timeline), tomorrow (expanded), this_week (collapsed), next_week (collapsed), later (collapsed), batch chips, someday tease. "All clear" empty state. Powered by `GET /inbox/brief`.
- **ExtractDetailModal:** Shows item detail + change history (from `GET /extracts/:id/history`), draft generation (for `follow_ups` items), copy + share buttons, snooze sheet (later today, tomorrow, weekend, next week, someday), calendar event info.
- **Calendar:** Settings → Calendar section. Google via `expo-web-browser` OAuth flow; Apple via `expo-calendar` on-device. Multiple Google accounts supported. `CalendarSection` component in `components/settings/`.
- **Real-time:** **`hooks/useDumpInboxStream.ts`** after dump → refresh inbox.
- **Timezone:** **`TimezoneRegistrar`** — PATCH **`/users/me/timezone`**.
- **Push:** **`PushNotificationRegistrar`** — **`inbox_updated`** → **`/inbox`**.
- **Dumps (Thoughts route):** Shows polished text only (no original dump shown to user). Label "Dumps" in nav — covers thoughts, journal entries, dictations, anything the user dumps.
- **Brand:** **`constants/theme.ts`**, **`typography.ts`**, **`brand/pem-brand.html`**.

## JSX readability

Prefer named booleans, early returns, small child components. Avoid nested ternary trees.

**Maintenance:** When **routes, UI patterns, tokens, hooks, or API shapes** change, update **this file** in the same effort. See **`pem-project.mdc`**.
